---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import Navigation from '../../components/Navigation.astro';
import Footer from '../../components/Footer.astro';
import SchemaMarkup from '../../components/SchemaMarkup.astro';
import Icon from '../../components/Icon.astro';

const publishDate = "November 26, 2025";
const author = "The Valley Clean Team";
const readTime = "8 min read";
---

<BaseLayout title="Pre-Thanksgiving Deep Cleaning Guide | Valley Clean Team" description="Thanksgiving cleaning checklist for Alabama and Tennessee homeowners. Prepare your home for holiday guests with pro tips.">
  <SchemaMarkup type="article" />
  <Navigation />

  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section class="pt-32 pb-12 px-6 bg-gradient-to-br from-gray-50 to-white">
    <div class="container mx-auto max-w-4xl">
      <div class="text-center mb-8">
        <span class="category-tag">Holiday Cleaning</span>
        <span class="text-gray-500 text-sm ml-4">
          <Icon name="calendar" class="w-5 h-5 mr-2" />{publishDate}
        </span>
        <span class="text-gray-500 text-sm ml-4">
          <Icon name="clock" class="w-5 h-5 mr-2" />{readTime}
        </span>
      </div>
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-bold mb-6 text-[#333333] text-center leading-tight">
        Pre-Thanksgiving Deep Cleaning Guide: Get Your Home <span class="gold-gradient">Guest-Ready</span>
      </h1>
      <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 text-center max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        Thanksgiving is just around the corner, and for many Alabama and Tennessee families, that means hosting loved ones for the biggest meal of the year. Here's your complete guide to preparing your home for holiday guests.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Main Content -->
  <article class="py-12 px-6">
    <div class="container mx-auto max-w-3xl">
      <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">

        <!-- Introduction -->
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-8">
          There's nothing quite like gathering around the table with family and friends for Thanksgiving dinner. But if you're the host, the weeks leading up to Turkey Day can feel overwhelming. Between planning the menu, coordinating travel schedules, and managing everyday life, finding time to deep clean your home might seem impossible. That's why we've created this comprehensive guide to help you prepare your Huntsville, Nashville, Birmingham, or Muscle Shoals home for holiday guests—without the stress.
        </p>

        <!-- When to Start Section -->
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-[#333333] mt-12 mb-6">
          <Icon name="calendar-alt" class="w-5 h-5 text-[#FFA985] mr-3" />
          When Should You Start Cleaning for Thanksgiving?
        </h2>

        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-6">
          The key to stress-free holiday hosting is starting early. We recommend beginning your deep cleaning preparations <strong>1-2 weeks before your guests arrive</strong>. This timeline allows you to:
        </p>

        <ul class="space-y-3 mb-8">
          <li class="flex items-start">
            <Icon name="check-circle" class="w-5 h-5 text-[#FFA985] mr-3 mt-1" />
            <span class="text-gray-700">Tackle one room at a time without feeling rushed</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start">
            <Icon name="check-circle" class="w-5 h-5 text-[#FFA985] mr-3 mt-1" />
            <span class="text-gray-700">Address unexpected messes or repairs that pop up</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start">
            <Icon name="check-circle" class="w-5 h-5 text-[#FFA985] mr-3 mt-1" />
            <span class="text-gray-700">Save the final touches for the day before</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start">
            <Icon name="check-circle" class="w-5 h-5 text-[#FFA985] mr-3 mt-1" />
            <span class="text-gray-700">Actually enjoy the holiday instead of scrambling to clean</span>
          </li>
        </ul>

        <div class="bg-[#FFA985]/10 rounded-xl p-6 mb-8 border-l-4 border-[#FFA985]">
          <p class="text-gray-700 font-semibold mb-2">
            <Icon name="lightbulb" class="w-5 h-5 text-[#FFA985] mr-2" />Pro Tip:
          </p>
          <p class="text-gray-700">
            If you have overnight guests, clean guest rooms first—ideally 2-3 weeks out. These rooms typically see less daily traffic, so they'll stay clean until your guests arrive.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Priority Areas Section -->
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-[#333333] mt-12 mb-6">
          <Icon name="home" class="w-5 h-5 text-[#FFA985] mr-3" />
          Priority Areas: Where Your Guests Will Notice Most
        </h2>

        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-6">
          Let's be honest—you probably won't have time to deep clean every corner of your house before Thanksgiving. The good news? You don't have to. Focus your energy on these high-impact areas:
        </p>

        <!-- Kitchen -->
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-[#333333] mt-8 mb-4">
          1. The Kitchen: Heart of Thanksgiving
        </h3>

        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
          Your kitchen will be the busiest room in the house on Thanksgiving Day. From preparing the turkey to washing dishes, this space needs to be spotless and organized.
        </p>

        <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-xl p-6 mb-6">
          <h4 class="font-bold text-[#333333] mb-4">Kitchen Deep Cleaning Checklist:</h4>
          <ul class="space-y-2">
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <Icon name="square" class="w-3 h-3 text-[#FFA985] mr-3 mt-1" />
              <span class="text-gray-700">Clean inside the oven (crusty spills will smoke during cooking!)</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <Icon name="square" class="w-3 h-3 text-[#FFA985] mr-3 mt-1" />
              <span class="text-gray-700">Empty and wipe down the refrigerator to make room for leftovers</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <Icon name="square" class="w-3 h-3 text-[#FFA985] mr-3 mt-1" />
              <span class="text-gray-700">Degrease the stovetop and range hood</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <Icon name="square" class="w-3 h-3 text-[#FFA985] mr-3 mt-1" />
              <span class="text-gray-700">Clean and sanitize countertops and backsplashes</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <Icon name="square" class="w-3 h-3 text-[#FFA985] mr-3 mt-1" />
              <span class="text-gray-700">Scrub the sink and polish the faucet</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <Icon name="square" class="w-3 h-3 text-[#FFA985] mr-3 mt-1" />
              <span class="text-gray-700">Clean out crumbs from the toaster and microwave</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <Icon name="square" class="w-3 h-3 text-[#FFA985] mr-3 mt-1" />
              <span class="text-gray-700">Mop floors, including under the kitchen table</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <Icon name="square" class="w-3 h-3 text-[#FFA985] mr-3 mt-1" />
              <span class="text-gray-700">Run and empty the dishwasher before guests arrive</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <!-- Bathrooms -->
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-[#333333] mt-8 mb-4">
          2. Guest Bathrooms: First Impressions Matter
        </h3>

        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
          Nothing says "welcome" like a sparkling clean bathroom. Your guests will definitely notice—and appreciate—a fresh, well-stocked restroom.
        </p>

        <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-xl p-6 mb-6">
          <h4 class="font-bold text-[#333333] mb-4">Bathroom Deep Cleaning Checklist:</h4>
          <ul class="space-y-2">
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <Icon name="square" class="w-3 h-3 text-[#FFA985] mr-3 mt-1" />
              <span class="text-gray-700">Scrub and sanitize the toilet inside and out</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <Icon name="square" class="w-3 h-3 text-[#FFA985] mr-3 mt-1" />
              <span class="text-gray-700">Clean mirrors and glass until streak-free</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <Icon name="square" class="w-3 h-3 text-[#FFA985] mr-3 mt-1" />
              <span class="text-gray-700">Wipe down counters, faucets, and cabinet fronts</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <Icon name="square" class="w-3 h-3 text-[#FFA985] mr-3 mt-1" />
              <span class="text-gray-700">Scrub the shower/tub and remove soap scum</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <Icon name="square" class="w-3 h-3 text-[#FFA985] mr-3 mt-1" />
              <span class="text-gray-700">Put out fresh hand towels and bath towels</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <Icon name="square" class="w-3 h-3 text-[#FFA985] mr-3 mt-1" />
              <span class="text-gray-700">Stock up on toilet paper (more than you think you'll need!)</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <Icon name="square" class="w-3 h-3 text-[#FFA985] mr-3 mt-1" />
              <span class="text-gray-700">Add a nightlight for overnight guests</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <Icon name="square" class="w-3 h-3 text-[#FFA985] mr-3 mt-1" />
              <span class="text-gray-700">Mop floors and clean baseboards</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <!-- Living Room -->
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-[#333333] mt-8 mb-4">
          3. Living Room & Gathering Spaces
        </h3>

        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
          After dinner, everyone migrates to the living room to watch football, play games, or simply catch up. Make sure this space is cozy and clean.
        </p>

        <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-xl p-6 mb-6">
          <h4 class="font-bold text-[#333333] mb-4">Living Room Checklist:</h4>
          <ul class="space-y-2">
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <Icon name="square" class="w-3 h-3 text-[#FFA985] mr-3 mt-1" />
              <span class="text-gray-700">Declutter surfaces—remove mail, magazines, and random items</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <Icon name="square" class="w-3 h-3 text-[#FFA985] mr-3 mt-1" />
              <span class="text-gray-700">Dust all surfaces, shelves, and decorative items</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <Icon name="square" class="w-3 h-3 text-[#FFA985] mr-3 mt-1" />
              <span class="text-gray-700">Vacuum upholstery and under cushions</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <Icon name="square" class="w-3 h-3 text-[#FFA985] mr-3 mt-1" />
              <span class="text-gray-700">Wash throw pillows and blankets</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <Icon name="square" class="w-3 h-3 text-[#FFA985] mr-3 mt-1" />
              <span class="text-gray-700">Vacuum carpets and rugs (treat any stains)</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <Icon name="square" class="w-3 h-3 text-[#FFA985] mr-3 mt-1" />
              <span class="text-gray-700">Clean windows and glass doors</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <Icon name="square" class="w-3 h-3 text-[#FFA985] mr-3 mt-1" />
              <span class="text-gray-700">Wipe down TV screen and electronics</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <!-- Entryway -->
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-[#333333] mt-8 mb-4">
          4. The Entryway: Setting the Tone
        </h3>

        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
          The first thing guests see when they walk through your door sets the tone for their entire visit. A clean, organized entryway says "welcome home."
        </p>

        <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-xl p-6 mb-6">
          <h4 class="font-bold text-[#333333] mb-4">Entryway Checklist:</h4>
          <ul class="space-y-2">
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <Icon name="square" class="w-3 h-3 text-[#FFA985] mr-3 mt-1" />
              <span class="text-gray-700">Sweep and mop the floor or vacuum rugs</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <Icon name="square" class="w-3 h-3 text-[#FFA985] mr-3 mt-1" />
              <span class="text-gray-700">Clean the front door and door frame</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <Icon name="square" class="w-3 h-3 text-[#FFA985] mr-3 mt-1" />
              <span class="text-gray-700">Clear out the coat closet to make room for guests' jackets</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <Icon name="square" class="w-3 h-3 text-[#FFA985] mr-3 mt-1" />
              <span class="text-gray-700">Add a boot tray for wet or muddy shoes</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <Icon name="square" class="w-3 h-3 text-[#FFA985] mr-3 mt-1" />
              <span class="text-gray-700">Place a fresh doormat inside and outside</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <!-- Guest Bedroom Section -->
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-[#333333] mt-12 mb-6">
          <Icon name="bed" class="w-5 h-5 text-[#FFA985] mr-3" />
          Preparing for Overnight Guests
        </h2>

        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-6">
          If you have family traveling from out of town to your Huntsville, Nashville, or Birmingham home, you'll want to make them feel right at home. Here's how to prepare the perfect guest room:
        </p>

        <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-[#FFA985]/10 to-gray-100 rounded-xl p-6 mb-8">
          <h4 class="font-bold text-[#333333] mb-4">Guest Room Must-Dos:</h4>
          <ul class="space-y-3">
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <Icon name="check" class="w-5 h-5 text-green-500 mr-3 mt-1" />
              <span class="text-gray-700"><strong>Fresh linens:</strong> Wash all sheets, pillowcases, blankets, and duvet covers</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <Icon name="check" class="w-5 h-5 text-green-500 mr-3 mt-1" />
              <span class="text-gray-700"><strong>Clean floors:</strong> Vacuum carpets or mop hard floors—guests walk barefoot!</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <Icon name="check" class="w-5 h-5 text-green-500 mr-3 mt-1" />
              <span class="text-gray-700"><strong>Dust everything:</strong> Nightstands, dressers, lamps, ceiling fans</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <Icon name="check" class="w-5 h-5 text-green-500 mr-3 mt-1" />
              <span class="text-gray-700"><strong>Empty closet space:</strong> Leave hangers and drawer space for their belongings</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <Icon name="check" class="w-5 h-5 text-green-500 mr-3 mt-1" />
              <span class="text-gray-700"><strong>Add thoughtful touches:</strong> Extra blankets, bottled water, phone charger, Wi-Fi password</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <Icon name="check" class="w-5 h-5 text-green-500 mr-3 mt-1" />
              <span class="text-gray-700"><strong>Fresh air:</strong> Open windows briefly to air out the room before their arrival</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <!-- Day-Of Tips -->
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-[#333333] mt-12 mb-6">
          <Icon name="clock" class="w-5 h-5 text-[#FFA985] mr-3" />
          Thanksgiving Day: Last-Minute Tips
        </h2>

        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-6">
          The big day is here! Here are some quick tips to keep your home looking great while you're busy cooking:
        </p>

        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 mb-8">
          <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 shadow-md border border-gray-200">
            <h4 class="font-bold text-[#333333] mb-3">
              <Icon name="utensils" class="w-5 h-5 text-[#FFA985] mr-2" />In the Kitchen
            </h4>
            <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-700">
              <li>• Clean as you cook—wipe counters between tasks</li>
              <li>• Fill the sink with soapy water for quick soaks</li>
              <li>• Line trash cans with extra bags for easy changes</li>
              <li>• Run the dishwasher before guests arrive</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 shadow-md border border-gray-200">
            <h4 class="font-bold text-[#333333] mb-3">
              <Icon name="door-open" class="w-5 h-5 text-[#FFA985] mr-2" />Throughout the House
            </h4>
            <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-700">
              <li>• Do a quick bathroom check before guests arrive</li>
              <li>• Light a candle or use a subtle air freshener</li>
              <li>• Put out extra hand towels</li>
              <li>• Turn on welcoming lights at the entrance</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- When to Hire Professionals -->
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-[#333333] mt-12 mb-6">
          <Icon name="hands-helping" class="w-5 h-5 text-[#FFA985] mr-3" />
          When It Makes Sense to Hire Professional Cleaners
        </h2>

        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-6">
          Let's be real—between work, kids, and daily responsibilities, not everyone has time for a full pre-Thanksgiving deep clean. Here's when hiring a professional cleaning service like The Valley Clean Team makes sense:
        </p>

        <ul class="space-y-4 mb-8">
          <li class="flex items-start">
            <Icon name="check-circle" class="w-5 h-5 text-[#FFA985] mr-3 mt-1" />
            <span class="text-gray-700"><strong>You're hosting more than 10 guests</strong> and need help getting your home guest-ready</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start">
            <Icon name="check-circle" class="w-5 h-5 text-[#FFA985] mr-3 mt-1" />
            <span class="text-gray-700"><strong>Your kitchen appliances need serious attention</strong>—we can deep clean ovens, refrigerators, and more</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start">
            <Icon name="check-circle" class="w-5 h-5 text-[#FFA985] mr-3 mt-1" />
            <span class="text-gray-700"><strong>You want to enjoy the holiday</strong> instead of spending it cleaning</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start">
            <Icon name="check-circle" class="w-5 h-5 text-[#FFA985] mr-3 mt-1" />
            <span class="text-gray-700"><strong>You need a post-Thanksgiving cleanup</strong> after everyone goes home</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start">
            <Icon name="check-circle" class="w-5 h-5 text-[#FFA985] mr-3 mt-1" />
            <span class="text-gray-700"><strong>You're hosting out-of-town guests</strong> and want pristine guest rooms</span>
          </li>
        </ul>

        <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-[#333333] to-[#1a1a2e] rounded-2xl p-8 text-white mb-8">
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 text-center">
            <Icon name="star" class="w-5 h-5 text-[#FFA985] mr-2" fill="currentColor" />
            Let Us Handle the Cleaning—You Handle the Turkey
          </h3>
          <p class="text-gray-300 text-center mb-6">
            The Valley Clean Team serves Huntsville, Nashville, Birmingham, Muscle Shoals, and surrounding areas. Book your pre-Thanksgiving deep clean today and spend the holiday focused on what really matters—family.
          </p>
          <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
            <a href="tel:2568261100" class="bg-gradient-to-r from-[#FFA985] to-[#FFC67D] text-[#333333] px-8 py-4 rounded-full font-bold text-center shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transition">
              <Icon name="phone" class="w-5 h-5 mr-2" />Call 256-826-1100
            </a>
            <a href="/contact" class="border-2 border-[#FFA985] text-[#FFA985] px-8 py-4 rounded-full font-bold text-center hover:bg-[#FFA985] hover:text-[#333333] transition">
              <Icon name="calendar" class="w-5 h-5 mr-2" />Book Online
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Conclusion -->
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-[#333333] mt-12 mb-6">
          Make This Thanksgiving Memorable (For the Right Reasons)
        </h2>

        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-6">
          Thanksgiving should be about gratitude, great food, and quality time with loved ones—not stressing over a messy house. Whether you tackle the cleaning yourself using our checklist or call in the professionals, the most important thing is creating a welcoming space where memories can be made.
        </p>

        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-6">
          From our family at The Valley Clean Team to yours, we wish you a happy, relaxing, and spotlessly clean Thanksgiving!
        </p>

        <!-- Author Box -->
        <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-xl p-6 mt-12 border border-gray-200">
          <div class="flex items-center">
            <div class="w-16 h-16 rounded-full bg-gradient-to-br from-[#FFA985] to-[#FFC67D] flex items-center justify-center mr-4">
              <Icon name="users" class="w-6 h-6 text-[#333333]" />
            </div>
            <div>
              <p class="font-bold text-[#333333]">{author}</p>
              <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Professional Cleaning Services in Alabama & Tennessee</p>
              <p class="text-gray-500 text-sm mt-1">Veteran-owned with 15+ years cleaning experience, serving 1,000+ happy customers</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </article>

